articles.title: Soldiers, Israeli peace activists clash as army blocks solidarity march to Huwara - The Times of Israel
articles.description: European diplomats also visit scene of settler rampage, call on Israel to bring to justice those behind the attack on West Bank Palestinian town
articles.content: Israel Defense Forces soldiers clashed with hundreds of left-wing Israeli activists trying to enter the West Bank Palestinian town of Huwara on a solidarity visit following a deadly settler rampage t… [+4697 chars]
